  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to qterminal</title>

    <para>
      The <application>qterminal</application> package contains a Qt widget
      based terminal emulator for <application>Qt</application> with support
      for multiple tabs.
    </para>

    &lfs82_checked;

